spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:description: The CoreAXI v3.0 is multi-master multiple-slave AXI3 bus interconnect. It provides 4 AXI MASTER interfaces and up to 16 AXI SLAVE interfaces. The number of AXI masters and slaves to be connected is programmable through parameter configuration. The IP core also provides feedthrough mode for single slave and single master configuration only.
